metadata.abstract: The document titled 'Ansprechpartner' provides a comprehensive list of key personnel within the VATSIM Germany organization. It includes names, functions, email addresses, and VATSIM IDs of various leaders and their deputies across different departments. The departments covered include vACC leadership, ATC training, pilot training, technical, PR & events, navigation, and pilot representation. Each entry specifies the role and contact information, ensuring that members can easily reach out to the appropriate person for their needs. Additionally, the document mentions that the leaders and deputies of the Flight Information Regions (FIRs) are also part of the staff, with their contact details available in the respective FIR sections.
